title: TriagerX workflow contains duplicate Assignees
body:
TriagerX workflow may contain duplicate Assignees when the issue is closed, e.g. https://github.com/eclipse-openj9/openj9/issues/20233#issuecomment-2380211634 listed `jdmpapin` twice:
```
PR Assignees: jdmpapin, jdmpapin, luke-li-2003, dsouzai, matthewhall2, Spencer-Comin
```
